This app is amazing! So easy to track feedings and pumping. I'm sure I will use the sleep recording when the little one gets older. For the previous reviewer with point two: you can see a log that correlates to the graph but there is no daily total--you have to add in your head. Seems easy enough for developers to just put a daily total number in the log or on top of the bar graph. I hope they make that change. Wonderful app otherwise.
This app helps a lot in parenting.
This app is very informative and nice to track baby feeding. Keep up the good work

This is a great app. I've been using it for three days, and I love it, especially as I'm now trying to figure out a schedule for my little one. The two reasons I didn't give it five stars: 1. I wish you could record what time the baby went to sleep without entering an ending time. For example, I put my baby to sleep for the night, but can't always remember the exact time that was when she wakes the next morning. 2. I wish you could pull daily totals in a simplified way. The only way I can look at totals are through a bar graph in increments of 5; it would be great to see simple daily totals without analyzing a graph.
Great tracker app. If there's a way that both parents can track same baby on two separate phones while syncing the info, that would give it 5 stars.
